@startuml current_005_render_flow
title UC Life Sim — render flow (Pixi ground + DOM HUD, HEAD)

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Inter, sans-serif"

package "ECS (active scene world)" as P_W #fff8ec {
  [world.query(...)] as Q
}

package "render/Game.tsx (React shell)" as P_GAME #e9f3ff {
  [useEffect: snapshot RAF] as RAF
  [PixiGroundRenderer ref] as REND_REF
  [host pointerdown\n→ MoveTarget on player] as CLICK_HOST
  [<PixiCanvas onReady={...}/>] as CANVAS
}

package "render/pixi" as P_PIXI #e9f3ff {
  [PixiCanvas (Application)] as PIXI_APP
}

package "render/ground" as P_GR #e9f3ff {
  [PixiGroundRenderer.ts] as GROUND
  [GroundSnapshot {\n roads, buildings, walls,\n doors, beds, barSeats,\n interactables, npcs, player }] as SNAP
}

package "render/sprite" as P_SP #e9f3ff {
  [appearanceToLpc.ts] as A2L
  [compose.ts (URLs under /lpc/)] as COMP
  [animTick.ts (RAF, decoupled\n from sim clock)] as ANIM
  [recolor.ts / palettes.ts] as REC
}

package "render/space" as P_SPC #e9f3ff {
  [PixiSpaceRenderer.ts]    as SPACE_R
  [PixiTacticalRenderer.ts] as TAC_R
  [particles.ts]            as PART
}

package "render/portrait (FC pregmod port)" as P_PT #f3e6ff {
  [react/Portrait.tsx] as P_REACT
}

package "ui/* (DOM HUD, React + zustand)" as P_UI #e9f3ff {
  [Hud / StatusPanel / ActionStatus] as HUD
  [ShopModal / FlightModal / NPCDialog\n / PortraitModal / SystemMenu / …] as MODALS
  [SpaceView / TacticalView /\n EngagementModal] as SPACE_UI
  [useUI / useEventLog / cameraStore\n (zustand)] as STORES
}

CANVAS --> PIXI_APP : onReady(app, root)
RAF --> Q          : per-frame world.query() →\nbuild GroundSnapshot
RAF --> REND_REF   : renderer.update(snap, cam)
REND_REF --> GROUND
GROUND --> SNAP
GROUND --> A2L : NPC sprite layer
A2L --> COMP
COMP --> ANIM
GROUND --> REC

SPACE_R --> PIXI_APP
TAC_R   --> PIXI_APP
SPACE_UI --> SPACE_R
SPACE_UI --> TAC_R

HUD     --> Q : useQuery / useTrait\n(via koota/react)
MODALS  --> Q : useQuery / useTrait
MODALS  --> P_REACT : portraits
HUD     --> STORES
MODALS  --> STORES

CLICK_HOST --> Q : (background click only)\n→ set MoveTarget on IsPlayer

note right of GROUND
  NPC + interactable Pixi nodes carry
  their own pointerdown handlers
  (eventMode='static'). Background
  clicks bubble to CLICK_HOST. This
  killed the legacy O(N) Konva linear
  scan on every click.
end note

note right of RAF
  (DRIFT) Design/architecture.md says
  "useQuery to subscribe to renderable
  entities". Reality: HUD does that;
  Game.tsx (visual marks) deliberately
  uses per-frame snapshots instead, for
  Pixi perf. Diagram is canonical.
end note

note bottom of A2L
  appearanceToLpc.ts is the LPC seam.
  It reads the UC Appearance trait —
  i.e. ECS state — and emits LPC layer
  keys. Today this is a pure function
  living in render/, called from inside
  the snapshot loop.
end note

note bottom of P_PT
  Portrait pipeline detail is in
  006_portrait_pipeline.puml.
  React-side it's just a component.
end note

@enduml
